title: Custody
subTitle: A police constable's life takes a drastic turn when he is entrusted with producing a criminal in court. While the mobster remains under his custody, Shiva must dodge every threat to keep him alive.

title: Spy
subTitle: An agent investigates the death of his elder brother with the help of his fellow agents. However, his actions lead to the discovery of a nuclear plot against India.

title: What the Fish
subTitle: Sudha hands over the responsibility of her house and pet fish to her niece's fiance before leaving for a holiday. When she returns, all seems fine until she opens the bathroom door.

title: Son Of Devil
subTitle: When a man rescues a woman from several thugs, who are harassing her, she falls in love with him. However, she is unaware of his dark past and deep secrets.

title: Darling 2
subTitle: Five friends on a holiday in Valparai find their getaway turning eerie when they sense the haunting presence of a friend who recently died by suicide.

title: Crazy Singh
subTitle: Bittu, a village simpleton, falls in love with a modern Saumya. Chaos ensues when their contrasting families meet to fix their marriage.

title: Aaraattu
subTitle: An affluent man is called upon to hand over his vast plot of land to the government. However, situations take a turn when he brings the influential Neyyattinkara Gopan into the picture.

title: Kadamban
subTitle: Kadamban lives a peaceful life with the villagers in a remote forest in Tamil Nadu. Things take a turn when a business tycoon decides to drive his tribe out of the area in order to extract minerals.

title: Jaguar
subTitle: Krishna, an orphan medical student, lives a seemingly ordinary life. However, unbeknownst to people, he is a vigilante named Jaguar who pursues a certain group of people in order to kill them.

title: Surya's Saturday
subTitle: Surya, a young man with anger issues, channels his emotions on Saturdays, because of a promise to his deceased mother. However, things get complicated when he decides to confront a corrupt cop.

title: Sindhubaadh
subTitle: Thiru, a small-time thief, embarks on a daring mission to Thailand to rescue Vendba, his wife, from a human trafficking gang.

title: Madhagaja
subTitle: The wife of one of two rival dons sends her son to a distant land to shield him from their relentless feud. However, the son, raised as an orphan, eventually returns to the brutal world of violence.

title: Alluri
subTitle: Iqbal, an aspiring police candidate, embarks on a journey to follow in the footsteps of Alluri, an upright officer, and discovers valuable lessons along the way.

title: Jigarbaaz Khiladi
subTitle: Shiva arrives in Chennai from Canada and starts up a real estate business. However, things take a turn when he realises that he is being cheated by the people he trusts.

title: Gollu Aur Pappu
subTitle: Two brothers, Gollu and Pappu, confront Gustaad Khan, a terrorist, for blowing up their garage. However, he decides to take advantage of their innocence by making them deploy a bomb in Ludhiana.

title: Kasak
subTitle: A nurse receives praise for taking care of a coma patient. However, after the nurse gets married, tragedy quickly befalls him.

title: Mere Do Anmol Ratan
subTitle: A woman's child gets mixed with another newborn during a hospital fire. However, unable to tell the two apart, she raises both as her own.

title: Yuvaraj
subTitle: Yuva enrols in an engineering college after getting banned from his sport and picks up fights with local students. However, his life gets more strained when his father flees, owing a huge debt.

title: Sangharsh Aur Vijay
subTitle: Badri is the protector of Badrinath temple. However, when a woman falls in love with him, his guru decides against making Badri his successor.

title: Naa Saami Ranga
subTitle: A man gains great notoriety in his village for his unmatched strength and brutal nature, which makes him a target of antisocial elements with a ruthless agenda.

title: Buddy
subTitle: A terrible accident leaves Pallavi in a coma while her soul possesses the body of a teddy bear. With her organs in danger of being traded, she enlists the help of a pilot, Aditya.

title: M.S. Dhoni: The Untold Story
subTitle: M S Dhoni, a boy from Ranchi, aspires to play cricket for India. Though he initially tries to please his father by working for the Indian Railways, he ultimately decides to chase his dreams.

title: Inspector Vijay
subTitle: Vijay, an honest police officer, meets Samyukta at a cafe and falls in love with her. However, his life changes when he witnesses a kidnapping and ends up helping a lonely woman, Lavanya.

title: The Return Of Lion
subTitle: When a social worker dies, his son must not only avenge his death but also prove his innocence when the welfare fund money accumulated by his family goes missing.

title: Inspector Vikram
subTitle: Vikram, a police officer, strives hard to solve every case that comes his way. However, things take an unexpected turn when he encounters a criminal mastermind who runs an illegal drug operation.

title: Inspector Vikram

title: Shylock
subTitle: Prathapa, a producer, is indebted to Boss, a ruthless moneylender, but refuses to pay his dues. As a result, the latter decides to make his life miserable at every turn.

title: Prema Katha Chitram 2
subTitle: After learning that Sudheer is in love with another girl, Bindu commits suicide. However, things take a turn when she returns as a spirit and starts haunting Sudheer and his girlfriend.

title: Kochadaiyaan
subTitle: Rana, a belligerent warrior, declares war against his kingdom's ruler to avenge his father's death, unexpectedly making a new enemy in the process.

title: Spy
subTitle: An agent investigates the death of his elder brother with the help of his fellow agents. However, his actions lead to the discovery of a nuclear plot against India.

title: King of Kotha
subTitle: Heartbroken on being back-stabbed by his childhood friend, Raju, an influential man, runs away from his hometown, Kotha. Soon, to bring back order in the town, a police officer plots a plan.

title: Mawali Raaj
subTitle: In order to obtain a family of their own, two young children of two single parents devise a plan to bring them together.

title: The Family Star
subTitle: Govardhan, a diligent architect, longs for a partner who understands his commitment to his large family. When Indu, a new tenant, moves in, his life starts to unfold in a new direction.

title: Seetharama Kalyana
subTitle: Arya, a righteous man, falls in love with a small-town woman named Geetha, unaware of the obstacles that lie ahead for both of them.

title: Bhadrakaali
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Double Attack
subTitle: Siddharth and Charan, two lookalikes who are fighting their own battles against evildoers, cross paths and join forces to take down Rawat, a ruthless minister.
